citeinfo.title: BNDRY_BUSINESSUNITS

descript.abstract: This is a polygon theme indicating the extent of the four Business Units within Kruger National Park . The KNP falls under the authority of South African National Parks (www.parks-sa.co.za).
descript.purpose: For the KNP Scientific Services GIS database - for research and cartograhic products. This database is intended to be extended or incorporated into a future KNP "Regional GIS" node of SANP.

srcinfo.srccontr: Source data as supplied by Surveys and Mapping were converted by GIMS from ReGIS format to ARC/INFO coverages, cleaned and built (tolerances unknown). They were also edge-matched and the national datum transformation from Cape to Hartebeesthoek94 datum was applied with an accuracy higher than that of the actual data.
Roads and rivers from the source data were selected to form the boundaries of the Business Units.
